294
00:19:38,724 --> 00:19:40,184
<i>pengawal keselamatan Haun…</i>

295
00:19:40,267 --> 00:19:42,394
<i>Kalau begitu, itu dipanggil apa?</i>

296
00:19:42,478 --> 00:19:44,313
Saya anggap…

297
00:19:44,396 --> 00:19:45,856
sebagai risiko.

298
00:19:45,939 --> 00:19:48,025
<i>Seratus pengawal keselamatan Haun…</i>

299
00:19:48,108 --> 00:19:50,069
Mereka musnahkannya sebelum kita mula.

300
00:19:50,152 --> 00:19:51,612
<i>…dan mulakan protes sekarang.</i>

301
00:19:51,695 --> 00:19:52,988
