319
00:20:51,380 --> 00:20:53,090
<i>Saya sangat berterima kasih kepada</i>

320
00:20:53,173 --> 00:20:55,718
<i>CEO Samsan, Cik Seo
sebab berikan saya peluang ini.</i>

321
00:20:56,677 --> 00:20:58,095
