328
00:21:11,108 --> 00:21:13,152
- Beritahu apa?
<i>- Sebagai rakan niaga…</i>

329
00:21:21,368 --> 00:21:22,995
- Helo?
<i>- Awak ada di mana?</i>

330
00:21:23,078 --> 00:21:24,329
Saya?

331
00:21:24,413 --> 00:21:26,582
